articles.title: The 'doomed Phobos moon' is about the crash into Mars - indy100
articles.description: When NASA’s Perseverance Rover observed an image from Mars of its moon Phobos eclipsing the Sun, it was a reminder that the astronomical body is doomed to crash into the planet. Phobos is the closest of Mars’ two moons and it is due to fall out of orbit relat…
